directives, including COVID-19-related measures.\n‚Ä¢ Leave an area at the first sign of unrest, or if a crowd is forming.\n‚Ä¢ Monitor our Denmark alerts for updates.\n', '\nDenmark: Aalborg (North Denmark region): Plan journeys\nbypassing protest on 8 May\n', '1', '1', '', 'ty Alert -International SOS<riskinsights@internationalsos.com>\nSent on:Thursday, May 6,20217:13:47 PM\nTo: Akash.Tomar@gds.ey.com\nSubject:1traveller now -Notice: Denmark -Aalborg (North Denmark region): Plan journeys bypassing\nprotest on8May\n', NULL),
