(496, 'Chile', 'Crime Risk', 'internationalsos', '2021-05-12', 'Not Recieved', '\n‚Ä¢ Reconfirm the status of affected routes before setting out. Plan alternate routes\nbypassing the protest to minimise inconvenience and allow additional travel time.\n‚Ä¢ If travelling near the affected area, anticipate heightened security and follow all official\ndirectives.\n‚Ä¢ Do not attempt to cross any roadblocks erected by protesters, as this may prompt a\nhostile response. If you encounter a blockaded road, turn around and seek an\nalternative route to your destination.\n‚Ä¢ If in standstill traffic, keep valuables hidden in the trunk and keep windows and doors\nlocked.\n‚Ä¢ Monitor our alerts on Bolivia for updates.\n', '\nBolivia: Plan journeys accounting for disruption due to highway\nblockades\n', '2', '3', '', ' -Advisory: Bolivia -Plan journeys accounting fordisruption due to highway\nblockades\n', NULL),
