(587, 'France', 'Crime Risk', 'internationalsos', '2021-05-19', 'Not Recieved', '\n‚Ä¢ High crime rates pose a significant risk across the country. Familiarise yourself with the\ncrime risk areas of your destination prior to travel.\n‚Ä¢ Exercise heightened vigilance at all times and in all areas. Maintain a low profile, avoid\nsharing personal and travel details with strangers or displays of wealth.\n‚Ä¢ Criminals are commonly armed. If targeted, do nothing to resist or antagonise the\nassailant/s.\n‚Ä¢ If caught in the vicinity of an ongoing crime-related incident, immediately leave that\nlocation until the situation stabilises.\n‚Ä¢ Refer to the Crime section of our South Africa pages for further information.\n', '\nSouth Africa: Western Cape: Recent killings linked to extortion\ngangs reflect risk of violent crime, need for precautions\n', '5', '1', '', ' -Notice: South Africa - Western Cape: Recent killings linked to extortion gangs\nreflect risk ofviolent crime, need forprecautions\n', NULL),
