(595, 'Bahrain', 'Crime Risk', 'internationalsos', '2021-05-09', 'Not Recieved', '\n‚Ä¢ Continue to anticipate protests. Liaise with local contacts for further information on any\nrelated demonstrations in your area. Avoid all such events as a precaution and to\nminimise travel delays.\n‚Ä¢ If travelling in the vicinity of a protest site, reconfirm the status of routes before setting\nout and allow additional time for journeys.\n‚Ä¢ Minimise time spent in the vicinity of likely flashpoints, particularly the Shia Muslim-\nmajority neighbourhoods of Aali, Diraz, Saar and Sitra.\n‚Ä¢ Monitor our Bahrain alerts for updates.\n', '\nBahrain: Continue to anticipate, avoid protests demanding\nrelease of political prisoners\n', '7', '1', '', ' -Notice: Bahrain - Continue to anticipate, avoid protests demanding release of\npolitical prisoners\n', NULL),
